defaultExecutive Summary:
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThere are more than 6,500 level crossings in Britain. Every day they save thousands 
defaultof lives by protecting us from one of the busiest rail networks in the world.
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultNetwork Rail invests in a wide-ranging 
defaultprogramme
default, working with national and local 
defaultorganisations
default, to ensure that level crossings are safe and helping people use them correctly.
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThere have been a number of high profile and tragic incidents at level crossings over the years, suggesting more needs to be done to educate drivers about the risks at level crossings. Combining education with 'enforcement' will ensure compliance is maintained.
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq
default traffic enforcement systems are designed to help the Police discourage individuals from breaking the rules.
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultSome traffic offences are criminal and so enforced by the Police, others are civil offences and enforced by local authorities.
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultEnforcement activity is also carried out by private contractors, for example controlling parking on private land.
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq's
default history and core expertise stems from working with the Police and enforcement agencies to process traffic offences. Our systems are both secure and flexible.
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq's
default modular system can provide Network Rail and BTP with an integrated solution, which can provide adjudication, document management and automated workflow allowing offenders to be processed according to the severity of the offence, offering educational alternatives to 'Fixed Penalty'.
default&#xa0;default&#xa0;defaultIntroduction:default1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq
default seeks to drive safety enhancements for all road users through 
defaulteducation defaultand enforcement. defaultStarTraq
default software solutions are designed for processing different 
defaulttypes of offences and for delivering 
defaulttargeted online education. 21 of the UK's Police 
defaultForces use 
defaultStarTraq
default systems to process their traffic offences, improving their efficiency 
defaultwhile maintaining high road safety standards.
default2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThere are many reasons why people commit offences on the road: understanding 
defaultthese reasons is 
defaultkey
default to changing driver 
defaultbehaviour
default. For some, the certainty of 
defaultpunishment through effective enforcement of the law is the best deterrent to offending 
defaultor re-offending. Others respond positively to education that raises knowledge and 
defaultawareness of the potential dangers and impact of their actions.
default3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq
default solutions support both 
defaultenforcers defaultwho need to identify offenders and process 
defaultpenalties quickly and efficiently, and 
defaulteducators defaultwho require the ability to 
defaultidentify,
default 
defaultprofile and divert individuals to 
defaultprogrammes
default that are relevant to their particular offence 
defaultand psychological profile.
default4.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq
default solutions cover:
defaultEnforcement:default 
defaultStarTraq's
default back office solution automates the processing of 
defaultoffences, improving productivity and compliance. It can be used for both police 
defaultand civil enforcement;
defaultEducation:default 
defaultStarTraq
default software can be used to identify and divert appropriate 
defaultcandidates onto driver education 
defaultprogrammes
