default5.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq
default has a strong 12 year track record in the international enforcement 
defaultarena. 
defaultStarTraq
default pioneered a public/private partnership in the South African offence 
defaultmanagement industry in 1999, and entered the UK market in 2001. A 
defaultStarTraq
default 
defaultmodular system is now used by over 50% of the Police Forces England, Wales and 
defaultNorthern Ireland to automate traffic offence management.
default6.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq's
default contribution to the UK transport industry was 
defaultrecognised
default with a 'Highly 
defaultCommended' in the Technology Category of the 2008 National Transport Awards and 
defaultis shortlisted for the Transport Operator of the Year Award in the 2013 National 
defaultTransport Awards to be held in October 2013
default7.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq
default processes over 1 
defaultmillion defaulttraffic offences and handled over 
default2 million defaultdocuments annually.
default8.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultStarTraq
default solutions deliver a virtually paper free environment for our customers and the 
